Class PrunedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>
        • java.util.ArrayList<Prediction>
          • misc.PrunedList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Prediction>, Collection<Prediction>, List<Prediction>, RandomAccess

    public class PrunedList
extends ArrayList<Prediction>
    A list implementing the prune_n function as described in the thesis. It is guaranteed that the entries of the list are sorted by score in descending order. Note that this implementation is rather inefficient so reimplementing it might speed up the generation process.
